#!/bin/bash ########################################################### # The script acts as a wrapper script to determine which Akamai # to clear in Staging Environment. # Developed By: Chinmay Bhatawdekar (C.B) ###########################################################
AKUSER=saksapi AKPWD=t0uchd0wn1 AKTYPE=cpcode AKACTION=invalidate AKDOMAIN=staging AKURL=https://api.ccu.akamai.com/ccu/v2/queues/default echo "Akamai Content Clear" PURGEOPTS='{ "type" : "'${AKTYPE}'", "action" : "'${AKACTION}'", "domain" : "'${AKDOMAIN}'", "objects" : ["450878"] }'; curl $AKURL --proxy "proxy.saksdirect.com:80" -H "Content-Type:application/json" -d "${PURGEOPTS}" -u "$AKUSER:$AKPWD"

####################################### # Refresh Promo Service #######################################
for i in {1..2}; do echo "HOST promoservice-${i}"; curl "http://qao5apromoservicedeploy-promoservice-${i}.inst.qa-o5a.hbc-digital-1.cns.digital.hbc.com:9520/v1/promo-service/refresh" sleep 15 done
curl "http://qa-so5.digital.hbc.com/tool/loadPromoHashmap.jsp?bmForm=promo_hashmap_loader"

####################################### # Refresh Blue Martini Service #######################################
for i in {1..2}; do curl "hd1qxx2${i}lx.digital.hbc.com:7010/BMCache.jsp?bmcache_action=clear_all" done

####################################### # Clear Mobile Blue Martini Cache #######################################
for i in {1..2}; do echo "HOST hd1qxx2${i}lx.digital.hbc.com"; curl "http://hd1qxx2${i}lx.digital.hbc.com:7005/tools/BMCache.jsp?bmForm=clearCacheForm&bmFormID=lEzn0YT&bmUID=lEzn0YU&bmIsForm=true&bmPrevTemplate=%2FBMCache.jsp&bmArch=bmcache_action&bmcache_action=clear_all&bmSubmit=submit&submit=Clear&bmSubmit=submit" sleep 5 done
